I4Mjk2MjI0M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1778787954.73772", "card_id": "Q_2037211734738301895", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 GPT-image-2 生成偏魔幻、梦境、玄幻类题材容易出现「碎渣感」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有网友发现一个现象，如果「中国风」很重的图，或者有一些类似「游戏」、「原画」、「BlingBling 感」、「幻想」（就是偏魔幻色彩或者描述一个梦境大概的这种描述）这种就很容易出现这种所谓的「碎渣感」，虽然可能有时候一眼看不出来，但是你去看其他的图再返回来看就会有这种感觉。反而越是真实感系列的图，或者纯文本或者截图类的，就完全没有这种感觉。 被 OpenAI 图像生成核心大佬陈博远 私信回复「正在加班修复这个问题」。吐槽 GPT 新模型碎渣感，没想到 OpenAI 的大佬回复了 之前在 GPT Image 团队的研究科学家陈博远 @MIT 奶茶店长在知乎分享的「我在 OpenAI 修中文」的评论区，也有答主提过此问题。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-962b4ad0c2cc802b5115b6917fd6eeef_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037211734738301895"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI69jHov2dyOE+EAMaCTExOTQ2NjU5NyCnrobQBjAAOG5AFnITMjAzNzIxMTczNDczODMwMTg5NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1778787954.74397", "card_id": "Q_3161823405", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 190}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么在极地大乱斗经常看见出肉的小法？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c885c271cf0edb1a5c0e3496a9ba6e1d_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3161823405"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI69jHov2dyOE+EAMaCTExMTYwODkyNiDY96S5BjAAOMoBQBdyCjMxNjE4MjM0MDV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1778787954.74625", "card_id": "Q_2038039004210259865", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 247}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "武汉大学正式取消进校预约制，持身份证即可入校，此举会带来哪些影响？大学校园到底该怎么「敞开」才合适？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 13 日，武汉大学正式取消社会公众进校预约制度。公众无需任何预约，仅凭本人身份证即可在珞珈门、弘毅门步行入校，工作日及节假日均开放。这意味着学校自 2023 年 7 月实施的预约入校模式全面结束。公众进入武汉大学已无需预约，带上身份证即可进校"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b51b6045fb11b68ca41fe7bd5034f4e1_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038039004210259865"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI69jHov2dyOE+EAMaCTExOTQ5NzM5NyCbs5LQBjAAOM4DQBhyEzIwMzgwMzkwMDQyMTAyNTk4NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1778787954.75014", "card_id": "Q_1970144826889606913", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果你是小区业主，你支持成立业主委员会吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我们小区交付 6 年多，没有业主委员会。今年部分业主因物业使用大宗维修基金不透明推动成立业委会。另有部分业主反对成立业主委员会，担心业委会成立后会换成关系户物业，小区越搞越糟糕。目前的物业是开发商物业，整体的管理水平还可以。最终反对的业主获胜，成立业主委员会的动议搁浅。而现在尴尬的是，物业逐渐懈怠，一些举措业主不满意，又没有有效的克制措施。真是左右为难。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bed773fddb433b43c4d0452358a84e72.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1970144826889606913"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI69jHov2dyOE+EAMaCTExNzI0MzA5OSC6tLbIBjAAOFNAGXITMTk3MDE0NDgyNjg4OTYwNjkxM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1778787954.75393", "card_id": "Q_2036565240230454176", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 59}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "作为家长，你会叫孩子起床上学吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我觉得上学时间是固定的，孩子上学后就该有时间观念了。早上起床时间就该自己定，家长不应该再天天亲自叫他起床了。 如果孩子迟到，后果自负！ 我家偶尔叫一次，但基本不会刻意喊他起床上学。你们呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b178e19b9bd05a60ca9a7b44cccc59c2_b.jpg"}, "met